These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, indie, trance
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, dahlia
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, colonial
City: boston, hamburg, london
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, project-manager, librarian
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person traveling to boston is not the gothic-revival house##6
 2. the chef is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 4. the librarian is somewhere between the fan r&b and the person driving the skateboard##7
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 6. the fan indie is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the colonial house is not the project-manager##6
 8. the chef is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the colonial house##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is not the colonial house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre      | r&b       | indie  | trance     |
| Flower          | dahlia       | rose  | zinnia    |
| House         | farmhouse  | colonial   | gothic-revival |
| City   | boston | london   | hamburg     |
| Job   | chef  | librarian | project-manager   |
| Transport           | helicopter  | scooter      | skateboard  |

