3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall, chaman
1. the person playing chess is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the owner of the mouse##6
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
5. the person playing chess is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
7. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who likes purple##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's birthday is in january##7
9. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| Birthday      | october       | august      | january    |
| Pet          | guinea-pig     | mouse        | cat        |
| Color           | yellow  | purple | chestnut   |
| Hobby   | gardening | woodworking           | singing |
| Game   | domino  | mah-jongg    | chess   |
| Cigar     | chaman        | pall-mall          | aristoff         |

