The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite, iris
3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, monopoly
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growsdaisy##7
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fonseca-smoker##6
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the aristoff-smoker and the person playing monopoly##2
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
11. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

