.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, yellow, blue
3 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, ferret
House: victorian, futuristic, ranch-style
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, daffodil
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, argentine
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, apricot, peas
 1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
 2. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 4. the person eating artichoke is the person who likes blue##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 7. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
10. the argentine is the owner of the ferret##1
11. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
12. the malaysian is somewhere between the dutch and the person who growsdaffodil##7
13. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Color      | yellow | lilac         | blue  |
| Pet         | turtle  | bird | ferret  |
| House   | victorian      | futuristic       | ranch-style |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | azalea        | daffodil  |
| Nationality         | dutch    | malaysian  | argentine    |
| Food     | peas      | apricot   | artichoke    |

