.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, pop, r&b
City: new-york, nizza, venice
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, ebony, turquise
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, fanta
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, january
 1. the fan rock is not the person drinking tea##6
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes turquise##7
 4. the fan r&b is the person traveling to venice##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to venice##1
 6. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan rock##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
10. the person who likes black is the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre           | r&b    | rock | pop    |
| City   | venice       | nizza    | new-york   |
| Hobby   | chess        | card-games  | magic-tricks |
| Color           | turquise       | black   | ebony     |
| Beverage         | tea | fanta | soy-milk |
| Birthday     | july       | may | january    |

 